lept, the LORD God took out one of the man’s ribs and closed up the opening."}, {:version=>"English Standard Version", :text=>"So the LORD God caused a deep sleep to fall upon the man, and while he slept took one of his ribs and closed up its place with flesh."}, {:version=>"Berean Study Bible", :text=>"So the LORD God caused the man to fall into a deep sleep, and while he slept, He took one of the man’s ribs and closed up the area with flesh."}, {:version=>"New American Standard Bible ", :text=>"So the LORD God caused a deep sleep to fall upon the man, and he slept; then He took one of his ribs and closed up the flesh at that place."}, {:version=>"New King James Version", :text=>"And the LORD God caused a deep sleep to fall on Adam, and he slept; and He took one of his ribs, and closed up the flesh in its place."}, {:version=>"King James Bible", :text=>"And the LORD God caused a deep sleep to fall upon Adam, and he slept: and he took one of his ribs, and closed up the flesh instead thereof;"}, {:version=>"Christian Standard Bible", :text=>"So the LORD God caused a deep sleep to come over the man, and he slept. God took one of his ribs and closed the flesh at that place."}, {:version=>"Contemporary English Version", :text=>"So the LORD God made him fall into a deep sleep, and he took out one of the man's ribs. Then after closing the man's side, "}, {:version=>"Good News Translation", :text=>"Then the LORD God made the man fall into a deep sleep, and while he was sleeping, he took out one of the man's ribs and closed up the flesh. "}, {:version=>"Holman Christian Standard Bible", :text=>"So the LORD God caused a deep sleep to come over the man, and he slept. God took one of his ribs and closed the flesh at that place. "}, {:version=>"International Standard Version", :text=>"so the LORD God caused a deep sleep to overshadow the man. When the man was asleep, he removed one of the man's ribs and closed up the flesh where it had been. "}, {:version=>"NET Bible", :text=>"