ibs and closed up flesh in its stead."}, {:version=>"English Revised Version", :text=>"And the LORD God caused a deep sleep to fall upon the man, and he slept; and he took one of his ribs, and closed up the flesh instead thereof:"}, {:version=>"Webster's Bible Translation", :text=>"And the LORD God caused a deep sleep to fall upon Adam, and he slept; and he took one of his ribs, and closed up the flesh in its place."}, {:version=>"World English Bible", :text=>"Yahweh God caused a deep sleep to fall on the man, and he slept; and he took one of his ribs, and closed up the flesh in its place."}, {:version=>"Young's Literal Translation", :text=>" And Jehovah God causeth a deep sleep to fall upon the man, and he sleepeth, and He taketh one of his ribs, and closeth up flesh in its stead."}]}